body.description: Dapple Baby All Purpose Wipes are powered by plants to wipe away gunk, grime and sticky fingerprints from all of your household surfaces like toys, highchairs, swings, countertops and more. These plant-based, multi-surface wipes make cleaning around your house easy and worry-free. This powerful formula has been tested for product purity by the Clean Label Project, is hypoallergenic, Pediatrician and Dermatologist tested and made without harsh chemicals, parabens, sulfates, phthalates, mineral oil, synthetic dyes & fragrances, chlorine, alcohol, SLS, SLES, MEA, DEA, TEA.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Use for literally everything my baby touches
reviews.reviewText: This is a diaper bag must-have. I can’t leave the house without this so I have one in my purse, in my car, and my diaper bag. Leaves a nice scent, not overwhelming. Does a great job at cleaning messes/spills. Also never dry and not too wet which is a plus.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for Vacation
reviews.reviewText: I brought these with me when we stayed in a hotel recently and it brought me so much peace of mind. I used them on the airplane, at restaurants, and at our lodging. They didn’t dry out either!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lovely smell with trusted ingredients
reviews.reviewText: I actually enjoyed using these and will now be changing out my other house hold cleaning product wipes to this instead. This travel pack is easy to use on the go especially at parks and grocery stores. The scent is lovely and not over bearing like other brands.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars One is enough
reviews.reviewText: I ordered these wipes 2 months ago and I still have more than half in each pouch. (My baby is to young to make a big mess). I use them for on the go right now to wipe down changing stations, toys, counters and her stroller/car seat. Since the wipes are extremely moist I only have to use one for each wipe down. Dapple products complement my daughters sensitive skin while also cleaning at home and on the go.
